paragraph.text:
The term Indian Land has the same meaning given such term in 
              section 203(c)(3) of the Energy Policy Act of 2005 (
              Public Law 109–58
            ; 
              25 U.S.C. 3501
            ), including lands owned by Native Corporations under the 
              Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act (
              Public Law 92–203
            ; 
              43 U.S.C. 1601
            ).
